reviewText: I did not realize that this was geared more to men, I will give it as a gift to someone.
Not a fan of these dvds. I do lots of sit up videos and these were not ones I liked.

I lent out my last DVD on Abs exercises and it was never returned. Having bought this set as replacement DVDs I am actually quite glad. This set is so much better and enjoyable to follow. Having already been an Abs exercise fan, the CD for beginners was fairly routine, but the Intermediate and Advanced CDs are certainly working my Abs as they have never been worked before.

Probably the Best ab video I have purchased!! I got this video shortly after I had my second baby and couldn't be happier!! It pays to buy a GOOD video as opposed to a fad video or a celebrity video. There are plenty of breaks in between movement series to catch your breath and get ready for the next move.. (good for those of us who need a lot of breaks). It reminds me a lot of Beachbody Insanity Definitely recommend.
